Package: rogo
Title: A Tracery-like Replacement Grammar
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Vox",
           family = "Fields",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "foxfields0@gmail.com")
Description: Rogo is a Tracery-like replacement grammar implemented in R. Rogo
    generates text by traversing a grammar that is stored as a data table or
    CSV. Tracery was original created by Kate Compton for grammars stored in
    JSON files.
License: Apache 2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
